<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ك س ح:</span> <span class="c2">(الْأَكْسَحُ)</span> الْأَعْرَجُ وَالْمُقْعَدُ أَيْضًا.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«الصَّدَقَةُ مَالُ الْكُسْحَانِ وَالْعُورَانِ»</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>